ji\" />"},{"pid":"12619e17144c9a80de20b7d1c7ddff815eb17808","tid":13462,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"我3年前斷過一次前十字韌帶，前前後後要3個月先好返晒。私家做大約要8皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958989edc6984ad7d81d4b20d685e630c1c01564","tid":13462,"uid":30495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我3年前斷過一次前十字韌帶，前前後後要3個月先好返晒。私家做大約要8皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隻腳直唔直到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都私家就10皮"},{"pid":"719fe35bf519c7b395f6df34871eba8eaf4f21fa","tid":13462,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點知有冇傷到? 最近行山跑步到膝頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照磁力共振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去睇骨科 個醫生係咁屈下隻腳 仲按左啲位置就話冇事 畀左兩日藥食完都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39324cbe68bd3f01f139c1966c1dc6672ce32bfb","tid":13462,"uid":30495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點知有冇傷到? 最近行山跑步到膝頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照磁力共振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去睇骨科 個醫生係咁屈下隻腳 仲按左啲位置就話冇事 畀左兩日藥食完都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照下啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090300786ba197b851121a1e0fd6682580fd3035","tid":13462,"uid":38145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl